HOW TO : 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
1.Place EXTRACT_UI_ELEMENTS.exe inside the Qt project directory
2.Ensure the .ui file is present
3.Run the tool
4.Generated widget data and resize code will be created automatically
5.Integrate the generated code into your Qt application
